sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / Browser
    participant V as Django Views
    participant R as rag_service
    participant F as finetune_service
    participant D as document_builder
    participant PG as PostgreSQL + pgvector
    participant O as Ollama API

    note over U,O: ── Ask (Q&A) ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/query/
    V->>R: query_workflow_assistant(question)
    R->>O: POST /api/embed (nomic-embed-text)
    O-->>R: query vector [768]
    R->>PG: hybrid search (vec*0.62 + kw*0.38)
    PG-->>R: top-12 documents
    R->>O: POST /api/generate (llama3)
    O-->>R: answer text
    R-->>V: {answer, sources}
    V-->>U: JSON response

    note over U,O: ── Search (no LLM) ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/search/
    V->>F: search_rag_documents(query)
    F->>O: POST /api/embed (nomic-embed-text)
    O-->>F: query vector [768]
    F->>PG: hybrid search (vec*0.62 + kw*0.38)
    PG-->>F: ranked results
    F-->>V: {query, count, results}
    V-->>U: JSON response

    note over U,O: ── Generate (Robot Framework) ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/generate/
    V->>F: generate_test_script(prompt)
    F->>O: POST /api/generate (llama3-finetuned)
    O-->>F: .robot script text
    F-->>V: {script, model, elapsed_ms}
    V-->>U: JSON response

    note over U,O: ── Fine-tune: Build Dataset ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/finetune/ {action: build_dataset}
    V->>F: build_finetune_dataset()
    F->>PG: SELECT * FROM ai_rag_document
    PG-->>F: all embedded rows
    F-->>V: {count, jsonl}
    V-->>U: JSONL download

    note over U,O: ── Fine-tune: Create Model ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/finetune/ {action: create_model}
    V->>F: create_finetuned_model()
    F->>O: POST /api/create (FROM llama3 + SYSTEM prompt)
    O-->>F: ok
    F-->>V: {ok, model, base_model, elapsed_ms}
    V-->>U: JSON response

    note over U,O: ── Fine-tune: Check Status ──
    U->>V: GET /api/workflow-assistant/finetune/status/
    V->>F: get_finetune_status()
    F->>O: GET /api/tags
    O-->>F: model list
    F-->>V: {exists, model}
    V-->>U: JSON response

    note over U,O: ── Index Rebuild (background) ──
    U->>V: POST /api/workflow-assistant/rebuild/
    V->>R: queue_rag_rebuild()
    R->>R: set status=queued, spawn thread
    R->>D: build_rag_documents()
    D->>PG: SELECT steps, ai_workflow, ai_databank
    PG-->>D: source rows
    D-->>R: normalised documents
    R->>PG: TRUNCATE ai_rag_document_staging
    R->>PG: INSERT INTO ai_rag_document_staging
    loop each batch
        R->>O: POST /api/embed (nomic-embed-text)
        O-->>R: embeddings
        R->>PG: UPDATE staging SET embedding
        R->>PG: UPDATE ai_rag_sync_state (progress)
    end
    R->>PG: TRUNCATE ai_rag_document
    R->>PG: INSERT INTO ai_rag_document SELECT * FROM staging
    R->>PG: UPDATE ai_rag_sync_state → idle

    note over U,O: ── Poll Rebuild Status ──
    U->>V: GET /api/workflow-assistant/status/ (every 3s)
    V->>R: get_rag_status()
    R->>PG: SELECT FROM ai_rag_sync_state
    alt stale running (no live thread)
        R->>PG: reset status → idle
    end
    PG-->>R: {status, progress, counts}
    R-->>V: sync dict
    V-->>U: JSON response
